1353
01:04:20,791 --> 01:04:21,833
Ya, tapi tak apa-apa.

1354
01:04:21,916 --> 01:04:23,583
Jangan berurusan dengan mereka. Ayo.

1355
01:04:23,666 --> 01:04:25,250
Sial.

1356
01:04:25,333 --> 01:04:26,666
Ayolah, Jerome!

1357
01:04:26,750 --> 01:04:28,041
Aku lagi berusaha!

1358
01:04:29,125 --> 01:04:30,500
