Bapak-Bapak!

1367
01:04:55,375 --> 01:04:56,583
Di sini!

1368
01:05:01,041 --> 01:05:02,958
Mari kita lihat siapa penanggung jawabnya.

1369
01:05:03,041 --> 01:05:05,666
Siapa pun itu, dia akan... Sial!

1370
01:05:07,333 --> 01:05:09,625
- Ron! Cepat masuk!
- Sial!

1371
01:05:10,541 --> 01:05:11,583
Ayo pergi!

1372
